title: Clever Up! Building Block System 4.0
des: Welcome to HABA's Clever Up! Building System. The cubes, rectangular blocks, panels and strips make it possible to build, bridge and create inclines and levels. The balls bring color and ideas into play. The triangular prism allows for more complex, integrated constructions - roofs are also reinterpreted. Constructive and creative learning opens up a new universe of building blocks! Children also discover simple digital thinking.

title: Kullerbu Tractor and Trailer with Momentum Motor
des: The tractor with trailer drives over fields and meadows – as well as all Kullerbü play tracks. Plenty of farmyard fun! Guaranteed to make the hearts of little farmyard fans beat faster. Measures 7.5 long x 2.5 wide.

title: Kullerbu Bucket of 13 Assorted Wooden Balls
des: So many balls, so much rolling fun! But even the speediest balls need somewhere to rest. Up to 13 balls can sleep in this lightweight bucket. Contents: 1 ball bucket made from PP plastic and 13 colorful beech wood balls made from sustainable forestry and treated with non-toxic, water based stains. Ball measures 2 in diameter and is safe for children ages 2+.

title: Kullerbu Kringel Roundabout Play Track
des: Boundless Kullerbü driving fun with several connection points to which other Kullerbü trains can be easily grown. Even more driving fun with funny ball Pepe Arrow fast and fast-moving blue ball convertible. The Spielbahn Kringel roundabout can be built in three different variants.

title: Marine World Baby Soft Toys Bundle
des: This whimsical Marine World Baby Bundle includes 4 machine washable soft baby toys.     Discovery Cubes Marine World The fantastic marine world soft discovery blocks offer much more than just stacking. A rattle, mirror foil, clattering sound effects and crackling foil stimulate baby's senses and are an inspiration to play and explore. The bright colors and different materials and textures also open little ones to tactile and visual discovery. Each cube measures 3 x 3.

title: Marine World Fabric Rattle with Removable Teether Ring
des: This adorable marine themed rattle will delight babies with its sound effects. An easy to grasp removable rattle ring is the perfect size for baby. The detachable rattle ring by hook and loop faster makes this rattle easy to clean. This clutching toy is also safe for teething!. Washable fabric rattle with detachable plastic ring

title: Rainbow Fabric Baby Ball
des: Crinkles, textures and rattles too! Just the right amount of age-appropriate stimulation for your baby's development. Eight colorful fabric sections offer different textures, sounds, visual and auditory feedback: rough, smooth, ridges, solids, stripes, rustle, rattle, squeak, and more! Even the youngest babies love the rattling noise it makes when tossed in the air or rolled on the ground.

title: Terra Kids Cork Boat DIY Activity Kit
des: This boat takes only a short time to put together before it's ready to sail into uncharted waters in any weather. A great DIY activity for young and old alike! Made of environmentally friendly materials. The boat consists of compressed cork granules and is thus virtually unsinkable. Ideal for a weekend trip to the water or a family holiday on the beach or even the bath! Young boat builders can upgrade this cork vessel with elements they find lying around in nature. There are some great suggestions for this in the enclosed instruction booklet.

title: Terra Kids 22 Maxi Hand Glider
des: This glider flies through the air with ease with 2 different tail positions, for straight flight and loop de loops. Great for the rugged outdoors. Endless aviation fun! Simply hold the aircraft's shaft between thumb and pointer, take a running start and throw it into the air.

title: Terra Kids Camping Lantern
des: Whether your kids are camping out, spending the night in a tree house, going on a night hike or barbecuing around the campfire, this high-quality and sturdy camping lantern with its six LEDs always provides plenty of illumination. Turn it on by simply pulling the lamp-head out; turn off by closing it.

title: Ocean Fishing Fun Bath Toy with 5 Squirting Fish
des: These colorful fishy squirters tumble merrily through the water. Children can test their coordination using the fishing rod to cast out and hook them. How many can they collect? Promotes creative, imaginative fun in the bath! Set includes 5 fish squirters and one fishing rod made from sturdy plastic. (with hook and string included).

title: 3 Piece Stacking Boat Set
des: Bon Voyage! The stacking ships are ready to set sail through the bathtub or baby pool. Their shape allows them to easily ladle and scoop water, as well as next inside eachother for easy storage.

title: Bath Boat Mouse Ahoy!
des: For perfect bath or baby pool joy, give your child great bathtub toys! Here comes Sailor Mouse bringing hilarious bath time fun! Includes a finger puppet mouse and a boat that floats on the water's surface.

title: Paul and Pia Magic Color Changing Wash Away Bath Book
des: Playing outside is so much fun. But today, Paul and Pia got all muddy. In fact, they got dirt allover! No problem, because they will scrub up clean again in the bathtub. When they come into contact with warm water, all the dirty marks are gone in no time at all.

title: Spielstabil Small Sand & Snow Toys Bundle
des: Buy the bundle and save time shopping. Includes a small sand bucket, small sand sieve, and two small sand scoops, all in assorted colors. Great for snow too! Spielstabil products are made from food-grade ABS plastic and are PVC-free, Phthlate-free and BPA-Free.

title: Baudino Sand Glove Dinosaur
des: Our dinosaur is perfect for fostering your child’s interest in digging, especially for dinosaur bones, with this dinosaur head shovel. First bury the head of the dinosaur and then have fun excavating it like real archaeologists. When all dug up, wear it like a glove to take a bite out of the sand (dirt and snow too).

title: Sand Play Excavator
des: Made for fun in the sun, this colorful, eye catching excavator is sure to give your little one hours of fun at the beach, in the pool, or the sandbox. Your child can easily fill the hinged sand shovel with sand, shells, stones or any small item they wish to move. A simple locking mechanism keeps the shovel wide open when while scooping and closed tightly while transporting. The large wheels allow the truck to roll smoothly in the sand and the large handle allows your little one to easily carry the excavator to pour sand where needed.

title: Children's Long Handled Heavy Duty Beach Shovel
des: The minute you pick up this shovel, you will notice the difference: heavier, sturdier, more substantial! Perfect for some serious digging in the sand, garden or even snow.

title: Children's Long Handled Garden Rake
des: High-quality garden rake, unbreakable and ready for your next yard project! Measures 30 tall. Your child will be eager to do their outdoor chores with the bright green kid sized rake. Made of PVC-free, phthalate-free plastic and backed with a 10 year manufacturer's guarantee.

title: 1.5 Liter Pail for Sand & Snow (assorted colors)
des: Easy to pour spout and small handle tab built in. You can stand on it - it will bend but won t break. Measures approximately 4 tall x 7 in diameter and holds 1.5 liters. Suitable for ages 18 months and up. Spielstabil Products are manufactured in Germany and are PVC free, Phthlate free and BPA Free.
